kcu105_core.hsys
	Contains the SBC core hsys file please don't get confused by name kcu105 it is for vcu118 only (Created its not present by default)

processor_subsystem/
	Contains the Processor hsys file (in this case processor_1x1x32.hsys)

acb_sram/
	In this version of Build it contains only acb_sram block and core.

pipes.aa/
	This Contains the pipes declarations used in SBC core and Processor core.

signals.aa/
	This Contains the signal declarations used in SBC core and Processor core.

In future other blocks such as acb_afb_complex etc., must be added in this location.

Note: 
	The Build.sh script must be executed inside Ajit-Toolchain inside docker as it contains Ahir related libraries.
